These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk, mirinda, tea
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, december, june, may
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, dog, frog
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, parkour, snowboarding, surfing
 1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
 2. the person drinking milk is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 7. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 8. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 9. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
11. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |   4   |
| Beverage    | mirinda   | milk       | almond-milk | tea   |
| Birthday        | december    | may  | june      | april |
| Pet         | frog      | chinchilla | dog         | cat   |
| Sport   | rugby | parkour       | snowboarding        | surfing   |

