.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-2::.
4 different games are played: whist, billiard, snooker, poker
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, indian, malaysian, turkish
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, juice, mirinda, almond-milk
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, roller, tram, trike
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person playing billiard is the australian##1
3. the person driving the tram is the person playing snooker##1
4. the person playing whist is between the indian and the person driving the car##2
5. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is the person driving the trike##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
8. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
9. the indian is on the left of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |       3        |      4       |
| Game           | billiard | whist | poker | snooker |
| Nationality   | australian  | malaysian | indian         | turkish      |
| Beverage         | mirinda      | juice    | almond-milk         | milk   |
| Transport     | car         | roller    | trike          | tram         |

