3. the photographer is the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left##1
5. the person eating corn is the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the person eating spinach is on the far left or far right##3
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
8. the videographer is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person eating kiwi##2
9. the librarian is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4       |
