 2. the coach is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
 3. the townhouse house is on the left of the accountant##1
 4. the coach is on the right of the software-developer##1
 5. the palace house is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the palace house is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the coach##3
 8. the modern house is on the left of the teacher##1
 9. the accountant is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
10. the fan of trance is between the townhouse house and the fan of reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |
| House      | palace | townhouse | modern     | craftsman       |
| Job          | software-developer   | coach    | accountant | teacher       |
| Music-Genre   | funk     | metal       | trance    | reggae     |
