 2. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 3. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
 4. the owner of the rabbit is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the trike is between the person who growspoppy and the person who growsazalea##2
 6. the person who growstulip is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 7. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
 8. the owner of the rabbit is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 9. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
10. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the lizard is the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |      3      |     4      |
