 5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the futuristic house##1
 7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 9. the futuristic house is the person drinking tea##1
10. the modern house is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
11. the person watching zombie movies is the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3       |     4     |
| Hobby         | chess      | video-games | sudoku       | drawing   |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie     | documentary | martial-arts | animation |
| Beverage   | water    | sprite     | iced-tea        | tea       |
| House     | farmhouse | gothic-revival   | modern   | futuristic       |

