.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-20::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, lizard, guinea-pig, hedgehog
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, dancer, mechanic, scientist
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, gardening, sudoku, collecting
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, snowboarding, soccer, swimming
 1. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the analyst##1
 3. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 4. the dancer is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
 5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
 6. the person who's hobby is camping is between the dancer and the person who's sport is skiing##2
 7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the scientist##1
 8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 9. the owner of the guinea-pig is the dancer##1
10. the person who's hobby is camping is the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4     |
| Pet          | lizard | hedgehog   | guinea-pig   | goldfish |
| Job           | analyst   | mechanic     | dancer   | scientist |
| Hobby   | gardening    | camping    | collecting   | sudoku   |
| Sport         | skiing    | snowboarding | swimming | soccer    |

 